{"title":"诗三首","authors":["冀汸"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":2,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗三首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冀汸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春之声我看见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破旧的图画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂在屋角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——蛛丝织成的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粘满飞蛾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也听见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响在远方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——主旋律是迅雷疾风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨点为它伴奏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月的踪迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个圆圈套一个圆圈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留在树干中间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条波纹叠一条波纹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻在裸露的大山身上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逝去的流水不再回来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花还要重开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一天天老了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幼小者正在成长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过旧居"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鬼子投降的第二年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在这儿作客"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对面漂亮的小洋房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还留着耻辱的标志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“慰安所”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“最最最”的年月里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来“灭资院”看望友人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对面漂亮的小洋房——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“兴无楼”瞪大眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"监视我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今改变了模样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这座高楼，倚着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那座高楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地名还是吉庆街"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再叫“反修路”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}